              <flipboard active-id='3' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Seasonal Sales Trends Unveiled: Q3 Leads the Way with 19K&#10;Transactions, Showcasing a Peak in Consumer Purchasing.&#10;Following closely, Q2 and Q4 both present robust sales with&#10;11K transactions each, while Q1 marks the calm before the&#10;storm with 6K transactions. - Trejor6927 - 3/16/2026' captured-sheet='Step 2.1' id='1' />
                  <story-point caption='Sci/Fantasy Dominates the Charts: Holding 4 of the Top 10&#10;Spots in Reader Preferences. Mystery and Children&apos;s Genres&#10;Secure Their Appeal with 2 Spots Each. Young Adult and&#10;Romance, Not Far Behind, Claim Their Stake with 1 Spot Each.&#10;This Diverse Literary Landscape Reflects Varied Reader Tastes&#10;and the Rising Popularity of SciFi/Fantasy - Trejor6927 - 3/16/2026' captured-sheet='Step 2.2' id='2' />
                  <story-point caption='Ratings and Sales: An Emerging Pattern Suggests a Positive&#10;Correlation, Indicating That Books with Higher Ratings Tend to&#10;Attract More Orders, Though the Trend Is Not Uniform Across&#10;All Ratings. - Trejor6927 - 3/16/2026' captured-sheet='Step 2.3' id='3' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
